{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0001", "text": "人人望着你 以你做話題 樣貌未浪費", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 2, 5, 5, 5, 2, 2, 0, 2, 2, 2, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jan4", "jan4", "mong6", "zoek6", "nei5", "ji5", "nei5", "zou6", "waa6", "tai4", "joeng6", "maau6", "mei6", "long6", "fai3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "人人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "望", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "話題", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "樣貌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "浪費", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0002", "text": "你惹過那位 回頭便自縊 無愧萬人迷", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 4, 5, 2, 0, 0, 2, 2, 4, 0, 5, 2, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "je5", "gwo3", "naa5", "wai6", "wui4", "tau4", "bin6", "zi6", "ai3", "mou4", "kwai5", "maan6", "jan4", "mai4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "惹", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那位", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "回頭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自縊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無愧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "萬人迷", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0003", "text": "愛你若免費 豈非要感激上帝", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 2, 5, 4, 9, 3, 4, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["oi3", "nei5", "joek6", "min5", "fai3", "hei2", "fei1", "jiu3", "gam2", "gik1", "dai3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "免費", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "豈非", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感激", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上帝", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0004", "text": "戀人王 不用望 讓你引誘我的渴望", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 0, 0, 3, 2, 2, 2, 5, 5, 5, 5, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["lyun2", "jan4", "wong4", "bat1", "jung6", "mong6", "joeng6", "nei5", "jan5", "jau5", "ngo5", "dik1", "hot3", "mong6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "戀人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "王", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不用", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "望", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "引誘", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "渴望", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0005", "text": "戀人王 找寄託 由我囚禁也是娛樂", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 0, 0, 9, 4, 4, 0, 5, 0, 3, 5, 2, 0, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["lyun2", "jan4", "wong4", "zaau2", "gei3", "tok3", "jau4", "ngo5", "cau4", "gam1", "jaa5", "si6", "jyu4", "lok6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "戀人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "王", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "寄託", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "由", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "囚禁", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "娛樂", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0006", "text": "愛你令我兇惡 吻你是自私的傑作", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 2, 5, 3, 4, 5, 5, 2, 2, 3, 3, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["oi3", "nei5", "ling6", "ngo5", "hung1", "ok3", "man5", "nei5", "si6", "zi6", "si1", "dik1", "git6", "zok3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "令", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "兇惡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自私", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傑作", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "心肝命掟", "artists": ["鄭秀文"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1578", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YOR56eA5paH_MTU3OA_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
